nd school.</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-963_">In the UK alone, the Disability Discrimination Act (DDA) highlights the importance of accessibility, ensuring equal access to goods, services, and information for all citizens.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-965_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-966_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-967_">Recommendations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/people-in-a-technology-cyber-space-meeting-2023-11-27-05-20-14-utc.jpg?v=1710511206" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/people-in-a-technology-cyber-space-meeting-2023-11-27-05-20-14-utc.jpg?v=1710511206 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/people-in-a-technology-cyber-space-meeting-2023-11-27-05-20-14-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1710511206 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/people-in-a-technology-cyber-space-meeting-2023-11-27-05-20-14-utc_500x.jpg?v=1710511206 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Inclusive Education Empowerment: Navigating Global Accessibility Awareness Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Inclusive Education Empowerment: Navigating Global Accessibility Awareness Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-969_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-970_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-972_"><li tabindex="0" 